You sum up my feelings about this whole thing pretty well. I am thinking already of changing how I play this character in order to merely survive. Such as, you don't SoW me, I don't pull. Even if you do SoW me, depending on the zone, I still won't pull.  If I do pull, I'm going to FD as soon as I am back at the group and wait until whoever our tank may be engages mob for a while. Only then will I get up and do my damage. Otherwise I have to be healed a LOT because I take a LOT more damage now. Trouble is, this patch not only is forcing us to avoid aggro like the plague, it also nerfed our soloing ability. I chose this character because if you are careful you can solo decently. Now I can't even solo at all.<br>
